data.description: Stunning brick home found in the heart of Lewis Downs! 4 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms with a bonus room sets up as the perfect family home. Experience the luxury of tall ceilings, hardwood floors, and outdoor screened-in patio. Large owners suite with double vanities, walk-in closets, soaking tub on tile floors gives you all the feelings of comfort and relaxation. An open floor plan and spacious kitchen equipped with stainless steel appliances sets up great for entertaining around your outdoor firepit and fenced in backyard. A wonderful community with a pool and playground steps away.
